---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<Layout title="Weight Loss" description="Clinically supervised weight loss with GLP-1 evaluation, personalized plans, and ongoing monitoring. Telehealth across Florida.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-warm-light to-bg py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-block text-accent font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Weight Loss</span>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-primary-dark mb-6">Clinically supervised weight management</h1>
        <p class="text-text-light text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          A personalized approach to weight loss built around your health history, realistic goals, and real provider oversight — including GLP-1 receptor agonist evaluation for eligible patients.
        </p>
        <a href="https://mbsmedical.practicebetter.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-light text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-base font-semibold transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary/25">
          Book a Visit
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Three Phases -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading eyebrow="Our Approach" title="A structured path to your goals" subtitle="Three phases designed to evaluate, treat, and monitor your progress with clinical oversight at every step." />
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-8 bg-primary text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">1</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl text-primary-dark mb-3 mt-2">Initial Evaluation</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-light text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Comprehensive health history review including conditions, medications, and labs</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Realistic goal-setting based on your individual health profile</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Provider consultation discussing clinical options</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-8 bg-primary text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">2</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl text-primary-dark mb-3 mt-2">Medication-Assisted Weight Loss</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-light text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> GLP-1 receptor agonist evaluation for eligible patients</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Prescription management with dosing oversight and adjustments</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Ongoing provider review for effectiveness and side effects</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-8 bg-primary text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">3</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl text-primary-dark mb-3 mt-2">Ongoing Monitoring</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-light text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Scheduled progress check-ins with your provider</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Plan adjustments based on your response and goals</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Periodic lab monitoring of metabolic markers</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-warm-light">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading eyebrow="Common Questions" title="What to expect" />
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-primary-dark font-medium">
            Am I eligible for GLP-1 medication?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-text-light group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">Eligibility is determined on a case-by-case basis during your initial evaluation. Your provider will review your health history, current medications, and goals to determine if GLP-1 therapy is appropriate for you.</div>
        </details>
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-primary-dark font-medium">
            Do I need a referral?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-text-light group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">No referral is needed. You can book directly through our patient portal.</div>
        </details>
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-primary-dark font-medium">
            How often are follow-up visits?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-text-light group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">Follow-up frequency depends on your treatment type and how you're responding. Your provider will set a schedule that works for your plan.</div>
        </details>
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-primary-dark font-medium">
            Are lab costs included in the visit fee?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-text-light group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">Lab costs are separate from visit fees. Your provider will discuss what labs are needed and approximate costs during your visit.</div>
        </details>
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-primary-dark font-medium">
            Can this integrate with my primary care?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-text-light group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">Absolutely. If you're also a primary care patient with MBS Medical, your weight loss program is managed alongside your other conditions by the same provider.</div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-primary">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white mb-4">Take the first step</h2>
      <p class="text-white/80 text-lg mb-10">Book your initial evaluation and start working with a provider who builds a plan around your goals.</p>
      <a href="https://mbsmedical.practicebetter.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white text-primary-dark px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-base font-semibold hover:bg-warm-light transition-all hover:shadow-lg">
        Book a Visit
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
